nodes.text: Meck Feem was a male Human scavenger who lived on Coruscant during the Cold War with the resurgent Sith Empire.

A Human male, Meck Feem lived on the planet Coruscant where he worked at the Senate Commercial District below the Senate Building during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. A scavenger, Feem made a living passing on his knowledge of his trade to those who wished to learn.
